simplesect.para:
Any of the standard "at-clauses" that are used appear in the order
                  @param, @return, @throws,
                  @deprecated, and these four types never appear with an empty
               description. When an at-clause doesn't fit on a single line, continuation lines are
               indented six (or more) spaces from the position of
               the @.
